                  <rs id="t18680406-358-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18680406-358-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18680406-358-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing a purse, containing 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. and six pieces of paper, of <persName id="t18680406-name-252" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18680406-name-252" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
